{
  "stem": "11174.5",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I don't remember at the moment the name.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It was called the liberty ships.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I think my ship was-- no, it was-- I don't remember now.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "November-- we were 16 days on the boat.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we arrived November the 2nd to Tacoma, Washington.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was a new world.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We felt very good to arriving here.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there were people-- Jewish people committee-- came out to greet us.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] First we passed-- we went through Canada-- Victoria, BC, a nice little beautiful town about 60,000.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Some Jewish people came there to greet us just to say hello.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But in Tacoma, some people were-- [INAUDIBLE] were too [? far from there?] so they took us into-- to Seattle, Washington so far to a-- to a Mr.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Gnute.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Was their name.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And there was a [NON-ENGLISH] there-- a very nice aristocratic family.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And feeded us with a supper.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then we went on a-- on the train a few days [INAUDIBLE] and arrived in Philadelphia [? on a Friday ?] to my cousin, which I never had met before.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they treated me very nicely.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was there from Friday to a week later Saturday night.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was a convention-- a [INAUDIBLE] convention.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Then [? suddenly ?] I went to Brooklyn, and I slept over really, in a-- I think there was a YMCH.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "A [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I slept all--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The YMHA.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The YM-- no, I think it was--",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "See, I think so.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I'm not sure.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I think it cost me a dollar.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that was it, and then I started to-- to-- this was another chapter which there's nothing dramatic much about it that has to do with-- with-- with this-- all this Holocaust.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But here, I straggle up.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I-- in 1956, January, we got married.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My wife.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[LAUGHS]",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
